org.eclipse.papyrus.sysml14.requirements

Interface Copy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DirectedRelationshipPropertyPath, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Trace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CopyImpl

    public interface Copy
extends Trace
    A representation of the model object 'Copy'. A Copy relationship is a dependency between a supplier requirement and a client requirement that specifies that the text of the client requirement is a read-only copy of the text of the supplier requirement.
    See Also:
    RequirementsPackage.getCopy()
